WEBVTT

00:01.805 --> 00:03.257
GORDON: <i>Previously on "Gotham"...</i>

00:03.328 --> 00:06.663
GORDON: The infected are being
killed all over the city.

00:08.203 --> 00:09.767
RA'S AL GHUL: I'm the one you seek.

00:09.837 --> 00:11.556
I am Ra's al Ghul.

00:12.660 --> 00:14.881
This man is your past.

00:14.943 --> 00:16.819
Now embrace your future.

00:18.812 --> 00:20.012
(screams)

00:21.682 --> 00:23.515
(Alfred gasping)

00:23.551 --> 00:26.644
- RA'S AL GHUL: Use the waters, Bruce.
- (coughs, gasps)

00:26.707 --> 00:29.511
OSWALD: You were the one time
I let love weaken me.

00:29.550 --> 00:32.668
I want you around as
a constant reminder to never

00:32.705 --> 00:34.037
make that mistake again.

00:34.073 --> 00:35.239
(screams)

00:37.476 --> 00:38.709
SELINA: I heard about Alfred.

00:38.744 --> 00:40.010
Is he gonna be okay?

00:40.045 --> 00:41.211
You don't give a damn about Alfred,

00:41.247 --> 00:42.780
and you sure as hell
don't care about me.

00:42.815 --> 00:43.847
I know you better than that.

00:43.883 --> 00:45.182
I thought you did.

00:45.217 --> 00:46.784
GORDON: Jonathan Crane's father
made a toxin

00:46.819 --> 00:49.019
from the adrenal glands of his victims

00:49.054 --> 00:51.455
- while they experienced terror.
- (screams)

00:51.490 --> 00:53.891
- What do you want?
- I'm tired of just surviving.

00:53.926 --> 00:55.225
I want more.

00:59.064 --> 01:00.197
I'm sorry, Alfred.

01:00.232 --> 01:02.866
I've been trying to find
who I am for so long.

01:02.902 --> 01:04.233
Who am I supposed to be?

01:04.269 --> 01:05.570
- Money! Now!
- (gasps)

01:09.443 --> 01:12.177
ALFRED: You need to find
your true north.

01:12.212 --> 01:15.029
And let that guide you.

01:15.053 --> 01:16.848
(thunder rumbles)

01:24.958 --> 01:26.958
♪ ♪

01:28.000 --> 01:34.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:40.106 --> 01:42.073
(man and woman laughing,
talking quietly)

01:47.214 --> 01:48.746
Money! Now!

01:48.797 --> 01:50.797
(woman exclaims)

01:57.123 --> 01:58.723
Hurry up, huh? Give me the ring.

02:03.263 --> 02:06.064
You have one chance. Walk away.

02:08.199 --> 02:09.598
Who's this?

02:10.437 --> 02:12.170
(woman screaming)

02:21.513 --> 02:23.213
License.

02:23.396 --> 02:25.357
I got a license.

02:29.523 --> 02:31.523
♪ ♪

02:39.032 --> 02:41.032
(bird wings flapping)

02:55.148 --> 02:57.148
♪ ♪

03:05.725 --> 03:10.937
<font color="#0080ff">Synced & corrected by</font> kinglouisxx
